folder: Chrystie Street & Delancey Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
No. 141 Chrystie Street, adjoining the S.W. corner of Delancey Street. This view shows the Camp Memorial Church organized in 1859, when the Bouverie was known as the "Promenade".
About 1920.
Brown Brothers.
